The top 7 events from Track and Field come to life like never before. Being an athletic champion requires dedication, coordination, and concentration. Do you have what it takes to be one ?Virtua Athlete 2k offers all the realism and excitement of a worlwide tournament without the sweat and pain, challenging you to use quick reflexes and split-second timing to master each of the events. This may be your only chance to prove your-self on the olympic track.
 
- 100m dash, 100m hurdle, 1500m dash, long jump, javelin throw, shot put and high jump. 

- athlete customization : build your own character using details like facial  characteristics, body type, clothing choice and more.